<br />
</p>

<p><b>Given</b>: PenHolder.RadiusCm = 3 Cm</p>

<p>PenHolder.HeightCm = 10.5 Cm</p>

<p>Competitors.Number = 35 Nos. </p>

<p><br />
<br />
</p>

<p><b>To Find</b>: Cardboard.AreaSqCm = ? </p>

<p><br />
