<p>PenHolder.SASqCm=(PenHolder.RadiusCm)*(22/7)*(2*PenHolder.HeightCm+PenHolder.RadiusCm) SqCm </p>

<p>PenHolder.SASqCm = 3*(22/7)*(2*10.5+3) SqCm</p>

<p>PenHolder.SASqCm = 226.28571 SqCm </p>

<p>PenHolder.SASqCm = 226.28 SqCm </p>

